{"tid":722042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奪命火警】觀龍樓單位起火 男子墮樓慘遭分屍","createTime":"2018-06-29T07:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T09:24:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b1815ba47fe0133a08725eaa50d12b273e0990","tid":722042,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"西環龍華街20號觀龍樓二座，清晨5時18分，41樓一個單位發生火警，冒出濃煙及火光熊熊。多名街坊發現報警及自行疏散，有住客手抱嬰兒逃生。<br />\n<br />\n消防員到場撲救前，一名中年男子突從高處墮下，跌落行人通道頂，慘遭分屍，殘肢留在通道頂及散落地下，當場死亡。消防動用一喉一煙帽隊撲救，約35分鐘後將火救熄。一男一女吸入濃煙不適送院。現場消息指是冷氣機起火，警方正在場調查。<br />\n<br />\n消防指現場火勢猛烈，單位嚴重焚毀，稍後消防搜索犬到場搜索證物，約11時許，法醫到場登上行人通道頂，搜索證物，稍後撿走兩袋證物離開。而下午約2時，政府化驗師到起火單位搜證。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/150122_9f8eaa2bd24d0ee1829f1482af0c95ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F150122_9f8eaa2bd24d0ee1829f1482af0c95ac.png&h=5ac6d061&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/150125_bb3a78d1fafb68bcd80c966a3037df63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F150125_bb3a78d1fafb68bcd80c966a3037df63.png&h=1c7e185b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180629/58377133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58377133&d=lsEX9PPb4EQpsGRAxbWuro9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c70e6e26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58377133&h=c1c1bb26\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180629/58377133</a>"},{"pid":"276e1bcfd1b98a0ff28be60fb99fbd5bc21e5368","tid":722042,"uid":54031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1273ada3a4057b96547ce9a32b8415ad743354","tid":722042,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"推post"}]}